- hfsplus module :
  builtin since Linux 2.6.38 ?

- dmg2img :
  site : http://vu1tur.eu.org/tools/
  direct download, latest version : http://vu1tur.eu.org/tools/dmg2img-1.6.4.tar.gz

- udisks2 :
  site : http://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/udisks/
  download : http://udisks.freedesktop.org/releases/
  direct download version 2.1.1 : http://udisks.freedesktop.org/releases/udisks-2.1.1.tar.bz2

- You need to be in the 'disk' group.

- Darling (optional : only needed to use --run)
  site : http://darling.dolezel.info/en/Darling
  download (command) : git clone --recursive git://github.com/LubosD/darling.git
  build : see http://darling.dolezel.info/en/Build
